It's a project about input Chinese into Linux
I start the project to study Linux and Agile. I will utilize Agile practice during the development. Moreover, I will try to record my Linux programming study during the developing process.

Feature:
1. Auto run component continous integration:
    copy git-howto/post-merge.sample to .git/hooks/post-merge to enable CCI automatic running after each pull
2. sprint.py is a script to start a new sprint
    sprint.py new

